  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[When Digivolving][When Attacking][Once Per Turn] You may
    return 1 card with [Hybrid] in its traits from this Digimon''s digivolution cards
    to your hand to return 1 of your opponent''s Digimon with the same level as the
    returned card to its owner''s hand. Trash all of the digivolution cards of that
